Module com.example.platformerplain
Package com.example.platformerplain.config

Class ScreenType.Constants

java.lang.Object
com.example.platformerplain.config.ScreenType.Constants
Enclosing class:
ScreenType
private static class ScreenType.Constants extends Object
The Constants class contains constant values for file paths to FXML files for different screens and the titles for each screen.

The constants defined in this class are:
  • MAIN_SCREEN_PATH - The file path for the main screen FXML.
  • OPTION_SCREEN_PATH - The file path for the options screen FXML.
  • INFO_SCREEN_PATH - The file path for the information screen FXML.
  • END_SCREEN_PATH - The file path for the end screen FXML.
  • MAIN_SCREEN_TITLE - The title of the main screen.
  • OPTION_SCREEN_TITLE - The title of the options screen.
  • INFO_SCREEN_TITLE - The title of the information screen.
  • END_SCREEN_TITLE - The title of the game over screen.
